# Welcome Command Script

## Description
This Python script allows you to send a custom welcome message when a new user joins your server. You can customize the message and include the user's name.

## How to Use
1. **Set up the bot**  
   Replace `YOUR_BOT_TOKEN` with your bot's token.  
   - Get the token from the [Discord Developer Portal](https://discord.com/developers/applications).

2. **Install `discord.py`**  
   Open a terminal and install the library with:
   ```bash
   pip install discord.py
